THIRD-PARTY SOURCE TEXTS

This project ingests and structures historical source texts. The texts
themselves are in the public domain by virtue of their age, but the
specific digitizations were obtained from the platforms below; we
acknowledge them out of academic courtesy and to allow downstream users
to verify our derivations.

  Source Text:    史记 (Records of the Grand Historian)
  Author:         司马迁 (Sima Qian)
  Composition:    ~104 — ~91 BCE (Western Han Dynasty)
  Status:         Public Domain (worldwide, by age)
  Digitization:   Chinese Text Project (CTP) — https://ctext.org/shiji/
  Files:          services/pipeline/fixtures/sources/shiji/*.txt
                  (each file's header records the specific ctext.org URL)
  Acknowledgment: We thank the Chinese Text Project for providing
                  open-access digitized editions of classical Chinese
                  texts. Per CTP's expressed wishes, academic uses are
                  encouraged to cite ctext.org as the digitization source.

